Original Draft - October 13, 2001<br>
Written by - Alihja Zanzibar<br>
Ratified by - All Administrators<br>
<br>
Part 1 - The purpose of these boards.<br>
<br>
The purpose of this EZboard is to allow the players of the Druzzil Ro server to come forth and discuss things which are related to the game EverQuest.  We wish to have an open and friendly atmousphere where players may come to talk about EverQuest and Druzzil Ro happenings (while they're not playing EverQuest).  It is not our intent to control nor dictate, but merely to moderate and make this board a pleasant place for all people, regardless of level, class, race or guild affiliation to interact with one another as a community.<br>
<br>
 <br>
With the utmost respect to our Druzzil Ro players and readers,<br>
(we wouldn't be here if it weren't for you all)<br>
<br>
 <br>
Part 2- The rules.<br>
<br>
These are the rules the administrators of druzzil-ro.net have discussed since the lifting of the bans on all posters on October 13, 2001.  These rules must be enforced unbiasedly and followed by all within the community regardless of guild status, relationship or affiliation to the druzzil-ro.net staff.  Any and all rules are subject to be modified, added to and/or edited as it is deemed neccessary by the druzzil-ro.net staff.  <br>
<br>
<br>
By posting here, you acknowledge that you will abide by these rules. <br>
Violations of these rules will result in the following:<br>
<br>
1st time-  Warning<br>
2nd time- Warning and 1 week ban<br>
3rd time- Sorry buddy... you're out!<br>
 <br>
Communication is the key to a friendly and fun server community.<br>
<br>
1) No spam. We may not delete it, but we'll edit and write over it to make it more funny. (unless you're selling magnetic immortality rings. That's funny all by itself)<br>
<br>
2) EZboard's ToS should be followed. Particularly, article 6 (USER CONDUCT) of the ToS. Everyone posting here has clicked &quot;agree&quot; to these terms (this rule was inspired by Verant... /salute)<br>
<br>
3) Posters should settle personal and guild wars in game, not in flame. Flaming will not result in anything positive.  If someone is a KSer or looted your no-drop breastplate.... Or, if a guild disrespected your planar raid reservations, we ask that you take it up with Verant, or that guild's leadership.. not with the entire community of Druzzil Ro.  We are moderators, but are not qualified to be mediators.<br>
<br>
4) Please don't try to make an ass of the moderators and admins. I personally know that I can do just fine on that all by myself. We don't need any help. Don't drive your admins or moderators nuts, or this could happen:<br>
<br>
pub73.ezboard.com/bsullonzektavern&lt;BR&gt;<br>
<br>
5) Profanity - (written but hardly enforced) There was a rule against profanity.. but if the admins don't follow it, why should anyone else? If certain people want to be percieved by others in that light, I'm not going stop anyone. &lt;BR&gt;<br>
<br>
6) There is no rule number 6.<br>
<br>
7) Posts about selling and trading accounts are not tolerated, as they violate the terms of service for EverQuest. - please don't do it.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->      Racial, religious, or ethnic slurs will not be tolerated.  <br>
<br>
9) Flames, and/or personal attacks upon a singular person or group of people, will not be tolerated.  Attack each other in private if you really can't control it.  There will be times where it will be neccessary to decide what is a personal attack and what isn't.  We wil use our best resources of logic and judgement should this situation arise..<br>
<br>
10)Internet/computer crimes and/or acts of internet terrorism against the website, ISP, email addresses located within, www.druzzil-ro.net will result in immediate banning with no warning.  Furthermore, such acts will be reported to the proper authorities.<br>
<br>
With all respect to you, the people of Druzzil Ro... we give a new start and a clean slate for all.<br>
